{"tid":975593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓職最正啦啦隊員曝光！22歲女甜笑網全倒　IG帳號神到了","createTime":"2019-01-09T18:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T02:15:15.000Z","uid":212399,"like":14,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"437c4a2742597f18bc18b04b57b1fda7cafe1d3b","tid":975593,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T18:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3822/d3822458.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3822%2Fd3822458.jpg&h=2d0c0e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲安智賢在韓職啦啦隊有很高的人氣。（圖／翻攝wlgus2qh&nbsp;IG，下同）<br />\n網搜小組／綜合報導<br />\n到場支援喜愛的球隊，絕對使許多死忠球迷必做的事，但場上站得激烈，途中也是需要啦啦隊的正妹們舒緩情緒。韓國一名22歲正妹安智賢（안지현）近日就因甜美的外表、賣力跳舞而爆紅，引起網友熱烈討論。<br />\n安智賢號稱是韓職人氣第一的啦啦隊正妹，除了天使般的臉蛋外，身材也是讓不少女生自嘆不如；另外，安智賢除了在職棒應援外，也是排球、籃球的啦啦隊，三棲的超人氣也讓她在棒球淡季持續爆紅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3822/d3822457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3822%2Fd3822457.jpg&h=f42c1cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼連台灣網友看完都戀愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3822/d3822456.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3822%2Fd3822456.jpg&h=38861c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n22歲的安智賢自曝光後，IG粉絲更有16萬之多，時常分享啦啦隊服以外的便服照，更被雜誌邀約，登上各大雜誌的封面，獲得「國民女神」的稱號。<br />\n許多台灣網友看完也直接被圈粉，「我老婆 謝謝」、「找他前先問一下他男朋友好嗎 啊對惹 就是我」、「明年拜託邀來桃園」、「她很有鄰家女孩的感覺」、「請各位祝福我們吧 ^.&lt;」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190109/1352502.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190109%2F1352502.htm&d=cdgV%2BFgls9bp56MrvvpdGWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d38c2fa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190109/1352502.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2cf14f533734c093b6d93a05ab89972e9c38f6ce","tid":975593,"uid":9470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T18:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab1eb151d3d45299ee9e716448155d91fe18723","tid":975593,"uid":101253,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T18:28:30.000Z","msg":"又係人造人"},{"pid":"ab1583bf789a6e6801f099468a1d081914183f45","tid":975593,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T18:31:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://instagram.com/wlgus2qh?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=wlmteyhpcfnn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fwlgus2qh%3Futm_source%3Dig_profile_share%26igshid%3Dwlmteyhpcfnn&d=cdgV%2BFgls9bp56MrvvpdGWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=3377a044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/wlgus2qh?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=wlmteyhpcfnn</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3060069f03eb80af73720e3be169bbca9cd01b","tid":975593,"uid":35430,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T18:31:21.000Z","msg":"一般靚妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c3f804834bae89e548d1e1c5989b3a57ed0c85","tid":975593,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T18:49:10.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"fb5138fe1aea27436305672b06fd69f2b429a562","tid":975593,"uid":39365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T19:12:47.000Z","msg":"真係好一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9042ec5725254018f277d75e468328e19449206d","tid":975593,"uid":190328,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T19:58:01.000Z","msg":"眼同鼻一撚定係假"},{"pid":"30655c905a73150f35ac64e0ba51f98e3e757956","tid":975593,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T20:01:50.000Z","msg":"好熟口面好似去韓國日日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/l